Constructors help us give initial values to the fields of a class.
Why we should use a constructors?
1)Constructors help us write cleaner code.
2) Constructors give us more control over the values that an wnd user can assign to the fields of a class.
Syntax of Constructors:
Access modifier Constructors same name as ClassName (Parameters){
}
Class Dog {
String name;
public Dog (String dogNAme){
name=dogName:
}